title: 'NOT for 15.6" laptops!!'
body: 'I tried with 3 laptops but None of my 15.6" laptops are even able to get packed inside the cover fully!! Can\'t even zip it cuz laptop edges are almost outside the cover. Misleading information given by the retailer..Maybe I didn\'t noticed cuz they mentioned range b/w 5"-5.6". Anyway it\'s definately not for 15.6" laptops. Thus returning back. Pros- Quality is good as per the price but size issue for me!!'

title: '"Highly Recommended: Durable and Convenient Laptop Bag with Ample Storage"'
body: 'I recently purchased a laptop bag and I am extremely satisfied with my purchase. The bag is made of high-quality materials and is designed to protect my laptop from any bumps or scratches. It also has ample storage space for other essentials such as a charger and mouse. The bag is lightweight making it easy to carry around. Overall I would highly recommend this laptop bag to anyone looking for a durable and convenient way to transport their laptop and accessories.'
